---
import SectionLayout from '../../layouts/SectionLayout.astro';
---

<SectionLayout title="La Loingtaine" section="about" activePage="history" description="La Loingtaine — an 18th century farmhouse near Fontainebleau dedicated to music, culture, and the arts.">
  <h2>La Loingtaine</h2>

  <div class="two-col">
    <div class="section-image">
      <img
        src="/images/site/home-hero.jpg"
        alt="La Loingtaine — an 18th century farmhouse near the forest of Fontainebleau"
        width="600"
        height="450"
        loading="eager"
      />
    </div>
    <div>
      <p>
        La Loingtaine is an <strong>18th-century farmhouse</strong> nestled near the
        forest of Fontainebleau, transformed into a living cultural space where music,
        ideas, and human connections flourish.
      </p>
      <p>
        More than a venue, it is a <strong>borderless space for intercultural dialogue</strong>,
        where musicians, thinkers, and audiences from around the world come together
        in an intimate, welcoming setting.
      </p>
      <p>
        Since 2005, La Loingtaine has hosted over 200 chamber music concerts,
        welcomed hundreds of young musicians through its academies and masterclasses,
        and facilitated countless conversations about art, science, and the human experience.
      </p>
      <p>
        The name "La Loingtaine" evokes both the place — <em>lointaine</em>, meaning "far away"
        in French — and the aspiration to reach beyond the everyday, toward something deeper
        and more meaningful.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</SectionLayout>

<style>
  .section-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(139, 117, 101, 0.2);
  }
</style>
